<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja" data-lang="ja">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>製造業特化 異常検知システム — ZetaX</title>
  <meta name="description" content="東大・東工大発のリザバーコンピューティング技術による次世代異常検知システム。GPU不要・クラウド不要のエッジAIで製造現場に実装します。">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@200;300;400;500;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <style is:global>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    :root {
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --bg-subtle: #f5f5f7;
      --bg-card: #f8f8f8;
      --text-primary: #111111;
      --text-secondary: #555555;
      --text-dim: #999999;
      --accent: #3B82F6;
      --accent-bright: #2563EB;
      --accent-glow: rgba(59,130,246,0.08);
      --accent-cyan: #0891B2;
      --silver: #888888;
      --font-jp: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      --font-en: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      --font-display: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      --transition: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 16px; background: var(--bg); overflow-x: hidden; }
    body { font-family: var(--font-jp); background: var(--bg); color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.8; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; overflow-x: hidden; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    .nav-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
    .nav-cta { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0e7490 0%, #0891b2 50%, #06b6d4 100%); color: #ffffff !important; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(8,145,178,0.3); transition: transform 0.2s var(--transition), box-shadow 0.2s var(--transition); white-space: nowrap; }
    .nav-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(8,145,178,0.4); }
    .lang-toggle { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.04); border-radius: 20px; padding: 3px; margin-left: 0; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .lang-btn { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 16px; border: none; cursor: pointer; background: transparent; color: var(--text-dim); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    .lang-btn.active { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(59,130,246,0.3); }
    .lang-btn:hover:not(.active) { color: #111111; }

    .nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1.2rem 3rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transition: box-shadow 0.3s; }
    .nav.scrolled { box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .nav-logo { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: #111111; }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: #666666; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: #111111; }

    .page-hero { padding: 11rem 2rem 5rem; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .page-hero { padding: 9rem 1.5rem 3rem; } }
    .page-label { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--accent-cyan); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: block; }
    .page-title { font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .page-desc { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.9; }

    .section { padding: 6rem 0; }
    .section-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
    .section-label { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--accent-cyan); text-transform: uppercase; display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .section-heading { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .section-text { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center; }
    .alt-bg { background: var(--bg-subtle); }

    /* CHALLENGE CARDS */
    .challenge-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .challenge-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; }
    .challenge-title { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .challenge-desc { font-size: 0.93rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.85; }

    /* STRENGTHS GRID */
    .strengths-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
    .strength-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid rgba(8,145,178,0.2); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; }
    .strength-title { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent-cyan); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .strength-desc { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.85; }

    /* TECH TAGS */
    .tech-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.75rem; justify-content: center; margin-top: 2rem; }
    .tech-tag { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-radius: 20px; padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }

    /* PLACEHOLDER */
    .placeholder-box { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border-radius: 12px; padding: 4rem 2rem; text-align: center; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.9rem; }

    /* RC PILLARS */
    .rc-pillars { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 3.5rem; }
    .rc-pillar { background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid rgba(8,145,178,0.18); border-radius: 14px; padding: 2.25rem 1.75rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: transform 0.4s var(--transition), box-shadow 0.4s var(--transition); }
    .rc-pillar::before { content: ""; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; width: 100%; height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-cyan), #06b6d4); }
    .rc-pillar:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(8,145,178,0.12); }
    .rc-pillar-num { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--accent-cyan); display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .rc-pillar-title { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.5; }
    .rc-pillar-desc { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.85; }

    /* RC FORMULA */
    .rc-formula { text-align: center; margin: 4rem auto 3rem; }
    .rc-formula-label { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--text-dim); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .rc-formula-text { font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 1.25rem; flex-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .rc-formula-text span { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-cyan), #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; }
    .rc-formula-text em { font-style: normal; color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 300; font-size: 0.85em; }

    /* RC USE CASES */
    .rc-uses { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .rc-use { background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
    .rc-use-highlight { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8,145,178,0.06) 0%, rgba(6,182,212,0.04) 100%); border: 1.5px solid rgba(8,145,178,0.3); transform: scale(1.03); }
    .rc-use-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.65rem; }
    .rc-use-highlight .rc-use-title { color: var(--accent-cyan); }
    .rc-use-desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.75; }

    .rc-footnote { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-dim); text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.85; max-width: 680px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

    /* MOBILE FLOATING CONTACT */
    .mobile-cta-bar { display: none; position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 99; padding: 0.75rem 1rem calc(0.75rem + env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0)); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08); box-shadow: 0 -4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
    .mobile-cta-btn { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem; width: 100%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0e7490 0%, #0891b2 50%, #06b6d4 100%); color: #ffffff; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; padding: 0.95rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(8,145,178,0.3); }
    .mobile-cta-btn::after { content: "→"; font-size: 1.1em; }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-section { position: relative; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0e7490 0%, #0891b2 50%, #06b6d4 100%); padding: 7rem 0; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; }
    .cta-section::before { content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 0%, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%); pointer-events: none; }
    .cta-section::after { content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0; background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px; pointer-events: none; }
    .cta-section .section-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .cta-heading { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.8vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: -0.01em; text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; background: #ffffff; color: #0e7490; font-family: var(--font-en); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em; padding: 1.05rem 2.8rem; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.25), 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); transition: transform 0.25s var(--transition), box-shadow 0.25s var(--transition); }
    .cta-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3), 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.18); }
    .cta-note { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin-top: 1.25rem; }

    .footer { padding: 2rem; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .footer-copy { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-dim); }

    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.7s var(--transition), transform 0.7s var(--transition); }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
    .reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
    .reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      body { padding-bottom: 5rem; }
      .nav { padding: 0.85rem 1rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .nav-actions { gap: 0.5rem; }
      .nav-cta { padding: 0.5rem 0.9rem; font-size: 0.72rem; }
      .section { padding: 4rem 1.25rem; }
      .section-inner { padding: 0; max-width: 100%; }
      .section-heading { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 2rem); line-height: 1.4; }
      .page-hero { padding: 9rem 1.25rem 2.5rem; }
      .page-title { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 6vw, 2.2rem); line-height: 1.4; }
      .page-desc { font-size: 0.92rem; }
      .feature-grid, .equipment-grid, .case-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 1rem; }
      .strengths-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 1rem; }
      .rc-pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; }
      .rc-pillar { padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem; }
      .rc-uses { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 0.85rem; }
      .rc-use-highlight { transform: none; }
      .rc-formula { margin: 2.5rem auto 2rem; }
      .rc-formula-text { gap: 0.85rem; font-size: 1.4rem; }
      .tech-tags { gap: 0.5rem; }
      .tech-tag { font-size: 0.78rem; padding: 0.45rem 0.85rem; }
      .cta-section { padding: 4.5rem 1.25rem; }
      .cta-heading { font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 5vw, 1.8rem); }
      .cta-btn { padding: 0.95rem 2rem; font-size: 0.92rem; }
      .mobile-cta-bar { display: block; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="nav" id="nav">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">ZETA<span>X</span></a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#solutions">Solutions</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#company">Company</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#news">News</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="nav-actions">
      <a href="/#contact" class="nav-cta" data-ja="お問い合わせ" data-en="Contact">お問い合わせ</a>
      <div class="lang-toggle">
        <button class="lang-btn active" data-lang="ja" onclick="switchLang('ja')">JP</button>
        <button class="lang-btn" data-lang="en" onclick="switchLang('en')">EN</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <div class="page-hero reveal">
    <span class="page-label">Anomaly Detection</span>
    <h1 class="page-title" data-ja="その異常、人が気づく前に検知する。" data-en="Detect anomalies before humans notice them.">その異常、人が気づく前に検知する。</h1>
    <p class="page-desc" data-ja="製造現場の「いつもと何か違う」を、リアルタイムで捉える。東大・東工大の研究から生まれた異常検知技術を、あなたの工場に実装します。" data-en="Capture the subtle shifts on your manufacturing floor in real time. We implement anomaly detection technology born from Tokyo and Tokyo Tech research.">製造現場の「いつもと何か違う」を、リアルタイムで捉える。東大・東工大の研究から生まれた異常検知技術を、あなたの工場に実装します。</p>
  </div>

  <!-- CHALLENGES -->
  <section class="section alt-bg">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="section-label">Challenges</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading" data-ja="こんなことありませんか？" data-en="Does this sound familiar?">こんなことありませんか？</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="challenge-list reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <h3 class="challenge-title" data-ja="壊れてから直す、の繰り返し。" data-en="Fix it after it breaks. Every time.">壊れてから直す、の繰り返し。</h3>
          <p class="challenge-desc" data-ja="異常に気づくのはラインが止まってから。計画外のダウンタイムが利益を削り、修理コストが積み上がる。" data-en="You notice the problem when the line stops. Unplanned downtime erodes profit. Repair costs pile up.">異常に気づくのはラインが止まってから。計画外のダウンタイムが利益を削り、修理コストが積み上がる。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <h3 class="challenge-title" data-ja="AI検知を入れたが、使われていない。" data-en="We installed AI detection. But nobody uses it.">AI検知を入れたが、使われていない。</h3>
          <p class="challenge-desc" data-ja="クラウド型のAI検知を導入したが、誤検知が多すぎて現場が信用しない。通信障害で止まることもある。結局、ベテランの巡回に戻っている。" data-en="Cloud-based AI detection had too many false alarms. The field doesn't trust it. Network failures cause outages. We're back to veteran inspections.">クラウド型のAI検知を導入したが、誤検知が多すぎて現場が信用しない。通信障害で止まることもある。結局、ベテランの巡回に戻っている。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <h3 class="challenge-title" data-ja="ベテランの「勘」が、引き継げない。" data-en="Veteran expertise can't be passed on.">ベテランの「勘」が、引き継げない。</h3>
          <p class="challenge-desc" data-ja="熟練者は音や振動の微妙な変化に気づく。でもその感覚は言語化できない。人が変われば、検知力も消える。" data-en="Experienced operators sense subtle vibration and sound changes. But that intuition can't be explained. When they leave, the detection ability vanishes.">熟練者は音や振動の微妙な変化に気づく。でもその感覚は言語化できない。人が変われば、検知力も消える。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- APPROACH -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center;">
        <span class="section-label">Our Approach</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading" data-ja="あなたの設備に最適化された、専用の検知モデルを作る。" data-en="We build a detection model optimized for your equipment.">あなたの設備に最適化された、専用の検知モデルを作る。</h2>
        <p class="section-text" data-ja="同じモーターでも、設置環境・稼働パターン・経年度合いで「正常」の基準は全く違います。汎用モデルを押し付けても精度は出ない。だから我々は、あなたの設備の正常稼働データから、その現場だけの検知モデルを構築します。" data-en="The same motor has different normal baselines depending on installation, usage patterns, and age. Generic models don't work. We build a model from your equipment's normal operating data—unique to your factory.">同じモーターでも、設置環境・稼働パターン・経年度合いで「正常」の基準は全く違います。汎用モデルを押し付けても精度は出ない。だから我々は、あなたの設備の正常稼働データから、その現場だけの検知モデルを構築します。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="strengths-grid reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="strength-card">
          <h3 class="strength-title" data-ja="GPU不要・クラウド不要" data-en="No GPU. No cloud.">GPU不要・クラウド不要</h3>
          <p class="strength-desc" data-ja="すべてエッジデバイス上で完結。製造データを外部に出さないから、セキュリティリスクがない。ネットワーク環境のない現場にも導入可能。" data-en="Everything runs on edge devices. Your manufacturing data never leaves your facility—zero security risk. Works even offline.">すべてエッジデバイス上で完結。製造データを外部に出さないから、セキュリティリスクがない。ネットワーク環境のない現場にも導入可能。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="strength-card">
          <h3 class="strength-title" data-ja="導入初日から検知開始" data-en="Detection starts on day one.">導入初日から検知開始</h3>
          <p class="strength-desc" data-ja="正常データのみで短時間にモデルを構築。大量の学習データを集める必要がない。" data-en="We build the model from normal data alone. No need to collect massive training datasets.">正常データのみで短時間にモデルを構築。大量の学習データを集める必要がない。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="strength-card">
          <h3 class="strength-title" data-ja="環境変化に自律追従" data-en="Adapts to environmental change">環境変化に自律追従</h3>
          <p class="strength-desc" data-ja="季節変動、設備の経年劣化、生産条件の変更にも常時再学習で対応。誤報の増加やモデルの陳腐化を防ぐ。" data-en="Continuous relearning handles seasonal shifts, equipment aging, and production changes. Prevents false alarm creep and model decay.">季節変動、設備の経年劣化、生産条件の変更にも常時再学習で対応。誤報の増加やモデルの陳腐化を防ぐ。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="strength-card">
          <h3 class="strength-title" data-ja="異常の理由が分かる" data-en="You understand why it alarmed">異常の理由が分かる</h3>
          <p class="strength-desc" data-ja="どのセンサー値が異常を示したか明確に表示。現場が納得して動ける。" data-en="We show exactly which sensor values triggered the alert. Your team acts with confidence.">どのセンサー値が異常を示したか明確に表示。現場が納得して動ける。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

